{
  "_tutorial_zh": [
    "=== 武器注册配置 ===",
    "此文件定义新武器的基础属性：类型、材质、伤害、耐久等",
    "",
    "字段说明：",
    "  id: 武器ID，必须唯一",
    "  type: 武器类型 (dagger/hammer/spear/battleaxe/nunchaku)",
    "  material: 材质定义",
    "    name: 材质名称",
    "    harvestLevel: 挖掘等级 (0-4)",
    "    durability: 耐久度",
    "    efficiency: 挖掘效率",
    "    damage: 基础伤害",
    "    enchantability: 附魔能力",
    "  damageModifier: 额外伤害加成 (可选)",
    "  speedModifier: 攻速修正值 (可选，负数=更快，正数=更慢。注意：这是内部值，不是UI显示值！)",
    "  texture: 纹理名称 (可选，默认使用id)"
  ],
  "_tutorial_en": [
    "=== Weapon Registration Config ===",
    "This file defines new weapon properties: type, material, damage, durability, etc.",
    "",
    "Fields:",
    "  id: Unique weapon ID",
    "  type: Weapon type (dagger/hammer/spear/battleaxe/nunchaku)",
    "  material: Material definition",
    "    name: Material name",
    "    harvestLevel: Mining level (0-4)",
    "    durability: Durability",
    "    efficiency: Mining speed",
    "    damage: Base damage",
    "    enchantability: Enchantability",
    "  damageModifier: Extra damage bonus (optional)",
    "  speedModifier: Attack speed modifier (optional, negative=faster, positive=slower. Note: this is internal value, not UI display!)",
    "  texture: Texture name (optional, defaults to id)"
  ],
